T : P_2 \rightarrow P_2
T(a_0 + a_1 x + a_2x^{2}) = (a_0 - a_1 - a_2) + (a_1 + a_2)x
a_0 + a_1 x + a_2x^{2},b_0 + b_1 x + b_2x^{2} \in P_2
\lambda \in \mathbb{R}
T((a_0 + a_1 x + a_2x^{2}) + (b_0 + b_1 x + b_2x^{2})) = T(a_0 + a_1 x + a_2x^{2}) + T(b_0 + b_1 x + b_2x^{2})
T(\lambda(a_0 + a_1 x + a_2x^{2})) = \lambda\ T(a_0 + a_1 x + a_2x^{2})
(a_0,a_1,a_2)^T
(a_0-a_1-a_2,a_1+a_2,0)^T
T((a_0,a_1,a_2)):=M\cdot(a_0,a_1,a_2)^T=(a_0-a_1-a_2,a_1+a_2,0)^T
 M= \begin{pmatrix} 1&-1&-1\\ 0&1&1\\ 0&0&0 \end{pmatrix} 
